biography: Katharine Jarmul is a Pythonista, data scientist and lover of Unix. Located in Berlin, Germany, she runs a data science consulting company Kjamistan. In her free time, she enjoys reading arXiv papers, organizing PyData Berlin and cooking spicy food.
